        "content": "<p>There must also be an argument parallel to the one I gave but phrased in the language of traditional universal algebra, since the argument works for any <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Variety_(universal_algebra)\">variety</a>.  However, I fear that in traditional universal algebra they'd have to muck around with a lot of syntax.</p>",
